Posset is equally good with blood oranges...the zest finely grated with sugar in food processor until the sugar is fragrant and brightly colored, then add to the cream and juice. I prefer it unstrained since the zest is so fine, others might prefer to strain. Love possets of all citrus varieties, lemon, lemon/orange, mandarin, lime, yuzu. Any crisp cookie, like a langue du chat, is a nice accompaniment.



